title: 118: The Pumpkin Haul Episode: September '20 Edition
itunes:title: The Pumpkin Haul Episode: September '20 Edition
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa and the gang are trying pumpkin food finds like pumpkin spice latte cold brew coffee, pumpkin pie ice cream sandwiches, pumpkin pie Kit Kat’s, pumpkin bread, and SO MUCH more! Plus, pumpkin finds from Hostess and our favorite brownie brittle maker, Sheila G! So jump right in, and when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: It’s finally pumpkin season!!! This week, we’re taste testing over a dozen pumpkin finds. Some were great, some were just so-so, and some were a big no-no!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
dc:creator: Lisa Lillien
